---
// About.astro
---
<section class="relative flex flex-col items-center max-w-screen-xl px-4 mx-auto md:flex-row sm:px-6 p-6 md:py-[40px] md:px-20" id="about">

    <div class="flex items-center py-4 md:w-5/12 md:pb-10 md:pt-6 md:pl-10 md:mr-8">
        <img src="/profile-picture.png" width="100%" alt="Precious Ajiboye — Technical Illustrator" loading="lazy"/>
    </div>

    <div class="row items-center py-4 md:w-7/12 md:pb-10 md:pt-6">
        <div class="text-left space-y-5">

            <h2 class="text-5xl font-normal sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tight font-display" style="color: #1E1D1A;">
                <span class="font-extrabold">About</span> me
            </h2>

            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed font-body" style="color: #6F6A63; max-width: 580px;">
                I'm Precious Ajiboye — a technical illustrator and visual communicator based in Barcelona. I specialise in turning complex ideas into clear, precise visuals across technical documentation, medical illustration, editorial design, and product communication.
            </p>

            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed font-body" style="color: #6F6A63; max-width: 580px;">
                My work spans instruction manuals, patent drawings, educational diagrams, fashion tech packs, and editorial spreads — always with a focus on accuracy, clarity, and visual purpose. I work with educators, publishers, startups, and product teams across Europe and beyond.
            </p>

            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed font-body" style="color: #6F6A63; max-width: 580px;">
                Whether it's clarifying a surgical procedure, documenting a garment construction, or building a visual identity for a product launch — I bring the same rigour and attention to detail to every brief.
            </p>

            <div class="pt-2">
                <a href="mailto:pregajii@gmail.com"
   class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-body font-medium text-white"
   style="background-color: #C46A4A; transition: background-color 300ms ease, transform 200ms ease;"
   onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#A3533A'; this.style.transform='translateY(-2px)';"
   onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='#C46A4A'; this.style.transform='translateY(0)';">
    Get In Touch
    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>
</a>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

</section>